" Hilight trailing whitespaces
:highlight ExtraWhitespace ctermbg=red guibg=red
:au BufWinEnter * let w:m1=matchadd('ExtraWhitespace', '\s\+$', -1)

" Ctrl+c pastes visual to clipboard
map <C-c> "+y<CR>

" Config file for coffeelint in syntastic
